// LeetCode 1598 - Crawler Log Folder
// https://leetcode.com/problems/crawler-log-folder/

/*
Logic:
Track current folder depth.

For each log:
- "../" → move back (depth-- if > 0)
- "./" → stay (do nothing)
- "x/" → move into folder (depth++)

Final depth = answer.

Stack approach simulates folders,
but simple counter works better.
*/


                  CODE

